headline.print_headline: Protesters Gather in Ferguson, Carry Signs, Chant
headline.main: Protesters Gather in Ferguson, Carry Signs, Chant

lead_paragraph: A huge crowd of people protesting the death of a black Missouri teenager shot by a white police officer have gathered in Ferguson, chanting and carrying signs.
